data.title: Movies of Theodor Loos and Sabine Peters together
data.meta_description: Movies of Theodor Loos and Sabine Peters together. Theodor Loos and Sabine Peters have worked together in the following movies. The first movie that Theodor Loos and Sabine Peters starred together was in 1932 and their last movie together was in 1937.
data.text:
Theodor Loos and Sabine Peters have starred in 2 movies together. Their first film was Acht Mädels im Boot in 1932. The most recent movie that Theodor Loos and Sabine Peters starred together was Die gläserne Kugel in 1937.
